hristmas-desserts-holiday-desserts-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EB%C3%BBche%20de%20No%C3%ABl%20recipe%3C%2Fa%3E%20featured%20spun%20sugar%20moss%20and%20meringue%20mushrooms%20atop%20the%20orange-flavored%20cake%20and%20chocolate%20frosting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20master%20French%20chef%20released%20several%20versions%20of%20the%20recipes%20used%20for%20her%20cake%20and%20frosting%20in%20this%20festive%20holiday%20creation.%20I%2C%20realizing%20I%20couldn't%20find%20exactly%20the%20version%20she%20used%20when%20she%20aired%20the%20original%20episode%20in%20season%203%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20French%20Chef%2C%26quot%3B%20used%20a%20slightly%20modified%20version%20from%20a%20cooking%20blog%20following%20along%20with%20the%20recipes%20from%20one%20of%20Julia's%20later%20books%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20Julia%20Child's%20Kitchen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20to%20take%20on%20the%20meringue%20mushrooms%2C%20but%20since%20the%20cake%20would%20travel%20nearly%20two%20hours%20by%20car%20with%20me%20to%20attend%20a%20holiday%20party%20at%20work%2C%20I%20omitted%20the%20spun%20sugar%20moss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chocolate%20frosting%20inside%20an%20orange%20cake%20being%20rolled%20into%20a%20log%20shape.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657d2dbb50edbc52a8650663%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20frosting%20came%20out%20a%20bit%20thinner%20than%20I'd%20anticipated%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20leak%20through%20the%20sides%20of%20my%20cake%20and%20it%20set%20up%20well%20in%20the%20fridge.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20made%20multiple%20recipes%20from%20Julia's%20triumphant%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fina-garten-and-julia-child-beef-bourguignon-compared-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMastering%20the%20Art%20of%20French%20Cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20series%20and%20am%20always%20amazed%20at%20how%20the%20flavors%20evolve%20as%20you%20go%20through%20the%20prescribed%20steps.%20This%20cake%20was%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20pulled%20it%20from%20the%20oven%2C%20carefully%20turning%20it%20onto%20a%20piece%20of%20parchment%20paper%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20tasted%20a%20few%20of%20the%20crumbled%20edges%20and%20the%20flavor%20was%20nothing%20special.%20The%20texture%20was%20a%20little%20unusual%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrainy%2C%20I%20think%20he%20called%20it.%20(He%20definitely%20did%2C%20I%20remember%2C%20just%20like%20I%20remember%20anything%20that%20could%20be%20considered%20even%20remotely%20negative%20that%20anyone%20says%20about%20my%20cooking.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20worried%20I'd%20misread%20something%20or%20that%20the%20humidity%20in%20my%20beach%20town%20had%20messed%20with%20the%20bake%2C%20especially%20since%20my%20cake%20felt%20like%20it%20turned%20out%20very%20thin%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20I%20once%20again%20put%20my%20faith%20in%20Julia's%20process%20and%20pushed%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20unfrosted%20yule%20log%20cake%20with%20a%20piece%20cut%20from%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657d2df850edbc52a8650666%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20rolled%20it%2C%20I%20was%20so%20excited%20it%20was%20keeping%20its%20shape%20I%20forgot%20how%20frustrated%20I'd%20been%20while%20making%20the%20frosting.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERolling%20the%20iconic%20log%20shape%20was%20easier%20with%20the%20large%2C%20thin%20cake.%20I%20had%20worried%20about%20cracking%2C%20a%20common%20pitfall%20among%20rolled%20cakes%2C%20but%20my%20sponge%20was%20workable%20and%20moist%20enough%20to%20be%20shaped%20without%20splitting%20down%20the%20middle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20worried%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhich-chocolate-frosting-is-best-taste-test-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echocolate%20frosting%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20made%20had%20too%20loose%20a%20texture%20(which%2C%20to%20be%20fair%2C%20it%20probably%20did%20because%20I%20mistakenly%20grabbed%20half%20and%20half%20instead%20of%20full-fat%20whipping%20cream%20at%20the%20store).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20less%20fat%20in%20the%20cream%2C%20the%20frosting%20didn't%20whip%20up%20as%20fluffy%20as%20it%20could%20have%20or%20as%20quickly%20as%20it%20typically%20would%2C%20but%20with%20a%20little%20extra%20cocoa%20powder%20and%20time%20in%20the%20fridge%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20the%20right%20consistency.%20It%20was%20spreadable%20without%20being%20runny%20and%20had%20a%20delicious%2C%20rich%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20meringue%20whipped%20to%20stiff%20peaks%20with%20an%20electric%20mixer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657d2d2c7a3c8094d5ddca57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20recipe%20requires%20you%20to%20create%20meringues%20for%20decoration%20and%20to%20incorporate%20into%20the%20frosting%2C%20which%20had%20both%20my%20mixers%20going%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meringues%20were%20where%20I%20started%20to%20lose%20it.%20It%20was%208%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20and%20I'd%20already%20been%20baking%20for%20over%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20making%20my%20way%20through%20a%20recipe%20with%20more%20than%20forty%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20little%20mushrooms%20to%20adorn%20the%20log%20cake%2C%20I%20piped%20rows%20of%20half-dollar-sized%20circles%20and%20stalks%20made%20of%20pieces%20that%20were%20meant%20to%20stand%20upright%20on%20their%20own.%20I%20hadn't%20worked%20with%20a%20piping%20bag%20in%20a%20while%20and%20was%20quickly%20frustrated%20that%20my%20skills%20weren't%20as%20sharp%20as%20my%20bakery%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20piping%20the%20mushroom%20shapes%2C%20I%20found%20the%20sticky%20texture%20of%20my%20meringue%20difficult%20to%20work%20with%20and%20was%20worried%20they%20wouldn't%20turn%20out%20right.%20But%20somehow%2C%20as%20tends%20to%20happen%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fjulie-powell-julie-and-julia-author-dies-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJulia's%20guidance%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20I%20doubt%20her%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0when%20I%20pulled%20them%20from%20the%20oven%2C%20the%20meringues%20turned%20out%20fluffy%20and%20light%2C%20melting%20perfectly%20in%20my%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20messy%20kitchen%20sink%20full%20of%20dishes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657d2e2d7a3c8094d5ddca63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulia%20Child's%20yule%20log%20recipe%20had%20me%20using%20almost%20every%20dish%20and%20baking%20utensil%20I%20had%20on%20hand.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20was%20done%20baking%2C%20I'd%20spent%20just%20over%20two%20hours%20puttering%20about%20the%20kitchen%2C%20dirtying%20every%20small%20bowl%20in%20the%20house%2C%20both%20the%20electric%20and%20stand%20mixer%2C%20piping%20bags%20and%20tips%2C%20measuring%20cups%20and%20spoons%2C%20a%20sifter%2C%20multiple%20baking%20sheets%2C%20mixing%20bowls%2C%20saucepans%2C%20a%20double%20boiler%2C%20and%20a%20candy%20thermometer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20sink%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fshould-you-rinse-dishes-before-putting-them-in-dishwasher-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilled%20with%20dishes%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20I'd%20spilled%20powdered%20sugar%20and%20cocoa%20on%20the%20counter%2C%20and%20frosting%20splattered%20across%20the%20stove.%20Still%2C%20I%20was%20left%20with%20the%20same%20warm%20feeling%20of%20accomplishment%20I%20usually%20experience%20when%20I've%20completed%20one%20of%20Julia's%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20trimmed%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20rolled%20cake%20before%20starting%20the%20decorating%20and%20shared%20the%20bonus%20bites%20with%20my%20partner%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0after%20the%20cake%20had%20rested%20and%20rolled%20with%20the%20frosting%20inside%2C%20the%20sponge%20was%20no%20longer%20grainy.%20Instead%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20whole%20thing%20was%20%26quot%3Bdelightful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20more%20what%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cake%20is%20displayed%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Culver%20City%20skyline.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657d25ad50edbc52a8650634%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20B%C3%BBche%20de%20No%C3%ABl%20is%20intended%20to%20look%20like%20a%20festive%20log%2C%20so%20it%20wasn't%20much%20to%20look%20at%2C%20even%20when%20decorated%20with%20powdered%20sugar%20and%20little%20meringue%20mushrooms%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20displayed%20triumphantly%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Culver%20City%20skyline.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20happens%20with%20most%20of%20her%20recipes%2C%20Julia%20took%20me%20through%20feelings%20of%20defeat%20and%20victory%2C%20ultimately%20leaving%20me%20feeling%20very%20proud%20that%20I'd%20tried%20something%20new%2C%20overcome%20challenges%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20and%20that%20the%20process%20had%20left%20me%20with%20something%20delicious%20to%20share%20with%20my%20colleagues%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saved%20the%20final%20decorations%20to%20complete%20just%20before%20serving%20in%20the%20office%20to%20prevent%20the%20sugar