%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ray's%20recipe%20used%20an%20array%20of%20ingredients%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20the%20soup%20didn't%20add%20much%20to%20the%20flavor%2C%20in%20my%20opinion.%20While%20I%20don't%20expect%20chicken%20noodle%20soup%20to%20reach%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhot-ones-challenge-sauces-what-its-actually-like-review-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHot%20Ones%26quot%3B%20levels%20of%20flavor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20initially%20hoped%20that%20the%20long%20list%20of%20ingredients%20would%20have%20produced%20a%20more%20noticeable%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20brighter%20note%2C%20I%20loved%20that%20the%20broth%20was%20airy%20and%20the%20chicken%20was%20incredibly%20tender.%20The%20leeks%20were%20also%20an%20interesting%20touch%20since%20I've%20never%20eaten%20them%20before.%20They%20reminded%20me%20of%20massive%20scallions%20while%20adding%20some%20nice%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELagasse's%20recipe%20uses%2015%20ingredients%2C%20including%20button%20mushrooms%20and%20vermicelli%20noodles.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emeril%20Lagassee's%20Chicken%20Noodle%20Soup%20ingredients.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579f1997a3c8094d5dc9907%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhoto%20showing%20ingredients%20needed%20for%20Emeril%20Lagasse's%20chicken%20noodle%20soup.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmonds%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20Lagasse's%20recipe%2C%20you'll%20need%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EOne%203-%20to%204-pound%20whole%20chicken%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E1%20quart%20chicken%20stock%20or%20low-sodium%20chicken%20broth%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E2%20quarts%20water%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E2%20medium%20onions%2C%20quartered%2C%20plus%201%2F2%20cup%20onions%2C%20diced%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E2%20carrots%2C%20rou