e%20six%20veggies%20and%20herbs%20he%20uses%20to%20make%20stock%3A%20onions%2C%20carrots%2C%20celery%2C%20thyme%2C%20parsley%2C%20and%20bay%20leaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20seasoned%20the%20stock%20with%20salt%20and%20pepper%2C%20brought%20the%20pot%20to%20a%20boil%20over%20high%20heat%2C%20and%20then%20reduced%20the%20heat%20to%20a%20simmer.%20Lagasse%20said%20to%20cook%20the%20chicken%20for%20one%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJust%20like%20Ray's%20recipe%2C%20you%20pull%20apart%20the%20chicken%20and%20carefully%20strain%20the%20broth.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emeril%20Lagasse's%20chicken%20noodle%20soup%20with%20broth.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579f2147a3c8094d5dc993c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221433%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKeep%20debris%20like%20onion%20and%20celery%20out%20of%20the%20broth%20(right).%20%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmonds%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20Lagasse%20suggested%20using%20tongs%20to%20remove%20the%20chicken%20from%20the%20broth%20and%20placing%20it%20onto%20a%20separate%20surface%20before%20shredding%20it.%20Let%20the%20chicken%20cool%20before%20removing%20the%20meat%20from%20the%20bones%2C%20skin%2C%20or%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20broth%2C%20use%20a%20fine%20mesh%20sieve%20to%20separate%20the%20broth%20from%20the%20cooked%20vegetables%20and%20herbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAdd%20mushrooms%20and%20a%20mirepoix%20into%20the%20Dutch%20oven%20over%20medium-high%20heat.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emeril%20Lagasse%20chicken%20noodle%20soup%2C%20mirepoix%20and%20butter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579f2587a3c8094d5dc995c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221432%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdd%20the%20mirepoix%20%E2%80%94%20onion%2C%20celery%2C%20and%20carrots%20%E2%80%94%20into%20the%20Dutch%20oven%20(left).%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmodns%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20Ray's%20recipe%20used%20leeks%20and%20parsnips%2C%20Lagasse%20upgraded%20his%20chicken%20noodle%20soup%20with%20button%20mushrooms.%20Add%20those%20mushrooms%20into%20the%20Dutch%20oven%20and%20cook%20until%20they've%20browned%20(keep%20an%20eye%20on%20them%20though%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20don't%20get%20too%20crisp).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20add%20the%20mirepoix%20%E2%80%94%20a%20culinary%20term%20for%20the%20onion%2C%20carrot%2C%20and%20celery%20combination%20%E2%80%94%20into%20the%20Dutch%20oven.%20It%20will%20take%20about%20four%20minutes%20to%20soften.%20Mix%20in%20the%20shredded%20chicken%20and%20butter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPour%20the%20broth%20into%20the%20Dutch%20oven%20and%20boil%20on%20high%20heat%20before%20adding%20vermicelli%20noodles.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emeril%20Lagasse%20chicken%20noodle%20soup%20boiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579f2b07a3c8094d5dc996d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221432%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECook%20the%20chicken%20noodle%20soup%20on%20simmer%20once%20all%20the%20ingredients%20are%20combined.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmonds%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20stood%20out%20in%20Lagasse's%20recipe%20was%20vermicelli%20noodles%2C%20which%20is%20a%20step%20away%20from%20the%20traditional%20egg%20noodles%20used%20in%20chicken%20noodle%20soups.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allrecipes.com%2Fwhat-is-vermicelli-7553587%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAll%20Recipes%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20vermicelli%20tends%20to%20be%20thicker%20in%20Italy%20but%20thinner%20in%20places%20like%20the%20United%20States.%20It's%20a%20bit%20more%20like%20angel%20hair%20pasta%2C%20making%20it%20lightweight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20tried%20this%20soup%20with%20thin%20noodles%2C%20but%20I%20love%20angel%20hair%20pasta%2C%20so%20I%20had%20high%20hopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPour%20the%20broth%20into%20the%20Dutch%20oven%2C%20combine%20it%20with%20the%20other%20ingredients%2C%20and%20boil%20over%20high%20heat.%20Then%2C%20reduce%20and%20simmer%20for%2030%20minutes.%20Add%20the%20vermicelli%20noodles%20into%20the%20broth%20with%20pepper%20and%20salt%2C%20cooking%20for%20about%2010%20minutes%20or%20until%20the%20noodles%20are%20soft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20remove%20the%20soup%20from%20heat%20and%20add%20some%20parsley%20as%20a%20garnish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20bam!%20Lagasse's%20chicken%20noodle%20soup%20is%20good%20to%20go.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emeril%20Lagassee%20chicken%20noodle%20soup%20recipe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579f2de7a3c8094d5dc9999%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20parsley%20added%20a%20nice%20garnish%20to%20the%20soup.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmonds%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20gripe%20with%20this%20recipe%20is%20that%20it%20takes%20two%20hours%2C%20but%20the%20bright%20side%20is%20that%20it%20wasn't%20arduous.%20Apart%20from%20shredding%20the%20chicken%20meat%20and%20chopping%20ingredients%2C%20the%20recipe%20mostly%20asked%20that%20the%20soup%20simmer%20for%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaste-wise%2C%20I%20thought%20Lagasse's%20broth%20was%20a%2010%20out%20of%2010.%20It%20was%20light%2C%20flavorful%2C%20and%20definitely%20exuded%20comfort%20food%20vibes.%20Adding%20store-bought%20stock%20to%20the%20broth%20was%20a%20great%20idea%20since%20it%20really%20drove%20home%20the%20chicken%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20liked%20the%20vermicelli%20noodles.%20I%20think%20noodles%20any%20thinner%20wouldn't%20have%20worked%2C%20but%20the%20vermicelli%20noodles%20were%20light%20while%20still%20absorbing%20that%20broth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELagasse's%20recipe%20took%20more%20time%20than%20Ray's%2C%20but%20it%20tasted%20better%20and%20used%20fewer%20ingredients%2C%20making%20this%20the%20recipe%20I%20would%20turn%20to%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-rachael-ray-emeril-lagasse-chicken-noodle-soup-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703336761000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579f7350ec98e92f74f1277%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-rachael-ray-emeril-lagasse-chicken-noodle-soup-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rachael%20Ray%20used%20leeks%20and%20parsnip%20to%20upgrade%20her%20soup%2C%20while%20Emeril%20Lagasse%20used%20mushrooms%20and%20vermicelli%20noodles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-rachael-ray-emeril-lagasse-chicken-noodle-soup-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel-Gaza%3A%20Israel%20says%20it%20has%20arrested%20hundreds%20of%20Hamas%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%20members%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703336363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F8807%2Fproduction%2F_132132843_gettyimages-1868362475-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67809242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Civilians%20are%20fleeing%20the%20Bureij%20refugee%20camp%20after%20Israel%20warned%20it%20was%20expanding%20its%20military%20campaign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A205%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67809242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67809242.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67809242.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20'The%20Iron%20Claw'%20director%20Sean%20Durkin%20made%20the%20Von%20Erich%20curse%20into%20a%20pro-wrestling%20Greek%20tragedy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zac%20Efron%20doing%20a%20drop%20kick%20in%20a%20wrestling%20ring%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F640f093eff11870018c4f6a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222731%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZac%20Efron%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EA24%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWarning%3A%20Spoilers%20ahead%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESean%20Durkin%20told%20BI%20about%20the%20challenges%20of%20bringing%20the%20Von%20Erich%20family's%20legacy%20to%20theaters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20scene%20in%20particular%20had%20the%20family%20of%20the%20surviving%20brother%2C%20Kevin%20Von%20Erich%2C%20in%20tears.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20countless%20tragic%20stories%20from%20the%20pro-wrestling%20world%2C%20but%20there's%20perhaps%20none%20as%20heartbreaking%20as%20the%20Von%20Erichs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20Texas%20and%20bred%20from%20birth%20to%20become%20wrestling%20titans%20by%20their%20father%2C%20former%20wrestler%20Fritz%20Von%20Erich%2C%20the%20four%20brothers%20%E2%80%94%20Kevin%20Von%20Erich%2C%20David%20Von%20Erich%2C%20Kerry%20Von%20Erich%2C%20and%20Mike%20Von%20Erich%20%E2%80%94%20were%20the%20main%20attractions%20at%20their%20dad's%20wrestling%20promotion%20World%20Class%20Championship%20Wrestling%20(WCCW)%20in%20the%20mid-1980s.%20They%20were%20considered%20golden-haired%20gods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20all%20the%20success%20and%20talent%2C%20there%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20dark%20cloud%20hanging%20over%20the%20siblings.%20By%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20only%20one%2C%20Kevin%2C%20was%20still%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20director%20Sean%20Durkin%2C%20a%20lifelong%20wrestling%20fan%2C%20the%20Von%20Erich%20story%20was%20right%20up%20his%20alley.%20Known%20in%20the%20indie-film%20world%20for%20his%20perfectly%20crafted%20slow-burn%20moody%20examinations%20of%20the%20human%20condition%20(%26quot%3BMartha%20Marcy%20May%20Marlene%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Nest%26quot%3B)%2C%20Durkin%20saw%20the%20legendary%20wrestling%20family%20as%20a%20modern-day%20Greek%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%2C%20David%2C%20and%20Kerry%20Von%20Erich%20standing%20shirtless%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6582fc21a79e5746976b795d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22372%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Kevin%2C%20David%2C%20and%20Kerry%20Von%20Erich.%3Cp%3EWorld%20Class%20Championship%20Wrestling%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw%26quot%3B%20chronicles%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20four%20brothers%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20their%20fame%2C%20which%20also%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20filled%20with%20sadness.%20(In%20reality%2C%20there%20were%20six%20brothers%20in%20total.%20Jack%20Jr.%20is%20briefly%20mentioned%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-iron-claw-why-chris-von-erich-isnt-in-movie-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChris%20is%20not.%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20span%20of%20nine%20years%2C%20David%20(played%20by%20Harris%20Dickinson)%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20a%20Tokyo%20hotel%20room%20due%20to%20enteritis%2C%20while%20Mike%20(Stanley%20Simons)%20and%20Kerry%20(Jeremy%20Allen%20White)%20committed%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDurkin%20puts%20the%20main%20focus%20on%20Kevin%20(Zac%20Efron)%2C%20the%20surviving%20brother.%20Through%20his%20eyes%2C%20we%20see%20a%20family%20soaring%20to%20huge%20heights%20under%20the%20tyrannical%20drive%20of%20their%20patriarch%20(played%20perfectly%20by%20Holt%20McCallany).%20Yet%2C%20all%20their%20dreams%20are%20dashed%20due%20to%20horrors%20that%20can%20only%20be%20summed%20up%20as%20a%20family%20curse%20on%20the%20level%20of%20Greek%20mythology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20chatted%20with%20Durkin%20about%20his%20eight-year%20journey%20to%20bring%20the%20Von%20Erich%20story%20to%20the%20screen%20and%20the%20scene%20that%20made%20the%20real%20Kevin's%20family%20the%20most%20emotional%20after%20seeing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20couldn't%20help%20but%20think%20how%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw%26quot%3B%20has%20similarities%20to%20your%20first%20movie%2C%20%26quot%3BMartha%20Marcy%20May%20Marlene%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20explored%20a%20cult.%20The%20Von%20Erich%20family%20very%20much%20had%20a%20cult%20mentality.%20Did%20you%20think%20that%20at%20all%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20and%20even%20with%20%26quot%3BThe%20Nest%26quot%3B%20as%20well.%20I%20guess%20I%20sort%20of%20believe%20all%20families%20have%20elements%20of%20cult%20in%20them.%20Just%20the%20way%20they%20operate%20as%20a%20family%20has%20a%20set%20of%20beliefs%20and%20most%20people%20fall%20into%20them%20and%20a%20couple%20people%20don't.%20It's%20about%2C%20how%20do%20those%20people%20find%20themselves%20even%20though%20they%20have%20been%20brought%20up%20in%20a%20certain%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20could%20probably%20make%20three%20different%20movies%20on%20the%20Von%20Erichs%20and%20they%20would%20all%20be%20great%2C%20that's%20just%20how%20much%20is%20in%20their%20legacy.%20Early%20in%20the%20process%2C%20did%20you%20come%20to%20peace%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20entire%20story%20in%20one%20telling%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20really.%20%5B%3Cem%3ELaughs%3C%2Fem%3E.%5D%20You%20come%20to%20peace%20with%20it%20eventually%2C%20but%20if%20you%20care%20at%20the%20level%20that%20I%20care%2C%20it's%20a%20really%20painful%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20start%20with%20this%20huge%20outline%20of%20life%20events%20and%20chip%20away%20at%20it%20and%20there's%20so%20many%20ways%20to%20go.%20Sometimes%20the%20core%20of%20the%20story%20shows%20itself%20to%20you%2C%20or%20you%20think%20it%20does%2C%20in%20the%20script%2C%20but%20then%20in%20the%20edit%2C%20it%20reveals%20itself%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sure%20there%20was%20a%20point%20where%20I%20had%20to%20decide%20which%20way%20I%20was%20going%20to%20go.%20It%20simply%20is%20making%20a%20choice%20and%20doing%20it.%20It's%20really%20difficult%2C%20especially%20with%20this%20story%2C%20because%20there%20are%20so%20many%20ways%20you%20could%20go.%20Endless%20ways.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zac%20Efron%2C%20Holt%20McCallany%2C%20Jeremey%20Allen%20White%2C%20and%20Harris%20Dickinson%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b3c7b7a3c8094d5dd045c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221954%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Zac%20Efron%2C%20Holt%20McCallany%2C%20Jeremey%20Allen%20White%2C%20and%20Harris%20Dickinson%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEric%20Chakeen%2FA24%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20all%20your%20movies%2C%20you've%20been%20able%20to%20develop%20a%20style%20and%20tone%20that%20makes%20the%20audience%20feel%20like%20you're%20living%20with%20these%20characters%2C%20you%20are%20intimately%20close%20with%20them.%20But%20then%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%20you%20bring%20an%20intimacy%20to%20the%20ring%20with%20the%20soft%20lighting%20and%20the%20dissolves.%20Was%20that%20your%20plan%20to%20have%20the%20ring%20itself%20stand%20out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah.%20And%20some%20of%20those%20dissolves%20were%20scripted.%20At%20times%2C%20things%20happen%20that%20lead%20each%20character%20on%20a%20different%20path%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20cross-fades%20to%20give%20it%20a%20haunted%20feeling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20the%20ring%20and%20the%20lighting%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20embrace%20where%20we%20were%20at.%20In%20the%20early%20days%20at%20the%20Sportatorium%2C%20it's%20a%20bit%20more%20raw%20and%20rough%20around%20the%20edges.%20But%20when%20it%20gets%20on%20TV%2C%20it%20becomes%20more%20defined%20and%20brighter.%20But%20then%20it%20gets%20colder%20towards%20the%20end%20when%20things%20aren't%20going%20well.%20So%20we%20definitely%20tried%20to%20light%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20matched%20the%20emotional%20trajectory%20of%20WCCW.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20three-face%20dissolve%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20bad-ass%20shots%20I've%20ever%20seen.%20Was%20that%20one%20scripted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20what%20was%20scripted%20was%20the%20face%20from%20each%20brother%20but%20to%20keep%20them%20all%20on%20and%20go%20three%20dissolves.%20I%20think%20that%20just%20happened%20early%20in%20the%20edit%20when%20we%20looked%20at%20the%20footage%20of%20that%20scene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zac%20Efron%20sweaty%20with%20no%20shirt%20on%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6582fed51c5c7b8c9a0a3b2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZac%20Efron%20as%20Kevin%20Von%20Erich%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EA24%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20think%20I've%20ever%20seen%20a%20three%20dissolve.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20haven't%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20your%20editor%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20nuts%20trying%20this.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20he%20might%20have%20even%20done%20it%20first!%20I%20can't%20remember.%20It%20was%20just%20one%20of%20those%20moments%20when%20you%20see%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20it's%20like%20magic.%20And%20emotionally%2C%20that%20moment%20in%20the%20movie%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20vibe%20that%20I%20was%20originally%20drawn%20to%20for%20the%20Von%20Erichs%20which%20was%20a%20mythical%20Greek%20tragedy.%20That%20scene%20is%20the%20choosing%20of%20the%20son.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%26quot%3BDark%20Side%20of%20the%20Ring%26quot%3B%20Von%20Erich%20episode%20came%20out%20years%20after%20you%20already%20began%20developing%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw.%26quot%3B%20When%20you%20saw%20that%2C%20were%20you%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BFuck%2C%20the%20story%20is%20already%20being%20told!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo.%20The%20opposite.%20The%20thing%20I%20was%20really%20struggling%20with%20when%20I%20started%20getting%20into%20this%20in%202015%2C%20was%20there%20was%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20wrestling%20journalism%20or%20thoughtful%20material%20about%20wrestling.%20There%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20books%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20journalists%2C%20but%20not%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20%26quot%3BDark%20Side%20of%20the%20Ring%26quot%3B%20came%20out%2C%20it%20just%20furthered%20that.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20watch%20that%20show.%20I%20was%20so%20psyched.%20And%20that%20also%20Kevin%20was%20getting%20that%20attention%20and%20the%20story%20was%20out%2C%20I%20think%20that%20helped%20not%20just%20the%20Von%20Erichs%20but%20wrestling%20itself%20to%20expand.%20The%20timing%20has%20only%20helped%20this%20film.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Faew-owner-tony-khan-interview-firing-cm-punk-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAEW%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20star%20MJF%20shows%20up%20for%20maybe%2030%20seconds%20in%20the%20movie%20as%20Lance%20Von%20Erich%2C%20a%20wrestler%20who%20wasn't%20part%20of%20the%20family%20but%20was%20given%20Von%20Erich%20as%20a%20stage%20name.%20The%20surviving%20brothers%20were%20always%20mad%20that%20he%20was%20given%20the%20moniker.%20Was%20there%20more%20of%20Lance%20that%20got%20cut%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20that%20was%20always%20planned%20to%20be%20just%20that.%20I%20was%20really%20interested%20in%20the%20Lance%20storyline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22865%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryan%20Nemeth%2C%20Sean%20Durkin%20and%20Maxwell%20Jacob%20Friedman%20at%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw%26quot%3B%20premiere%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6582fd1dcefc010bea2573a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22577%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Sean%20Durkin%20and%20MJF.%3Cp%3ETommaso%20Boddi%20%2F%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuch%20a%20crazy%20aspect%20of%20the%20Von%20Erich%20legacy.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20amazing%20storyline%20to%20have%20an%20imposter.%20But%20that%20didn't%20fit%20in%20the%20movie%20because%2C%20by%20that%20point%2C%20it's%20just%20about%20Kevin's%20emotional%20journey.%20Anything%20that's%20outside%20of%20Kevin's%20emotions%20would%20be%20a%20distraction%20to%20the%20core%20of%20the%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMax%20came%20in%20and%20he's%20the%20best.%20He%20did%20that%20for%20us%20and%20was%20also%20just%20a%20great%20voice%20in%20the%20process%20of%20what%20it's%20like%20in%20the%20business.%20Giving%20me%20detail%20of%20what%20it's%20like%20backstage%20and%20being%20on%20the%20road.%20There%20were%20a%20few%20key%20people%20who%20basically%20told%20me%20I%20was%20on%20the%20right%20track%2C%20and%20he%20was%20one%20of%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20moments%20in%20the%20movie%20is%20when%20Kerry%20meets%20his%20brothers%20in%20heaven.%20What%20was%20Kevin's%20reaction%20when%20he%20saw%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20I%20haven't%20talked%20about%20it%20but%20his%20kids%20have%20told%20me%20that%20