eed%20to%20keep%20digging%20holes%20our%20entire%20lives.%20We%20have%20made%20(the%20government)%20and%20India%20proud.%20This%20should%2C%20therefore%2C%20be%20a%20milestone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20Uttarakhand%20government%20of%20demeaning%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20rat-hole%20miners%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Cpropaganda-driven%E2%80%9D%20and%20of%20spreading%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%20rumours%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703335284000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01140335%2FGACaXNpbYAASMBx.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fno-inquiry-report-yet-but-silkyara-tunnel-work-resumes-rat-hole-miners-refuse-govt-reward-reports%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rat-hole%20miners%2C%20who%20dug%20through%20the%20last%2012%20meters%20when%20drilling%20machines%20failed%2C%20say%20Uttarakhand%20government%E2%80%99s%20award%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20each%20is%20not%20commensurate%20with%20the%20risk%20they%20took.%20They%20call%20it%20a%20'step-motherly%20treatment'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fno-inquiry-report-yet-but-silkyara-tunnel-work-resumes-rat-hole-miners-refuse-govt-reward-reports%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Money%20dysmorphia%3A%20Why%20some%20wealthy%20people%20don't%20feel%20like%20they're%20rich%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225254%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%226%20bundles%20of%20US%20%24100%20bills%20standing%20vertically%20on%20edge%20of%20white%20shelf%2C%20red%20background%5C%22%20c