%20love-hate%20relationship%20with%20the%20work%20culture%20here.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yuri%20Zanoni%20is%20a%2033-year-old%20tech%20worker%20from%20Brazil%2C%20who%20spent%20the%20past%20three%20years%20working%20for%20Chinese%20tech%20companies%20Alibaba%20and%20ByteDance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655f67ae4ca513d8242e0eb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYuri%20Zanoni%20is%20a%2033-year-old%20tech%20worker%20from%20Brazil%2C%20who%20has%20spent%20the%20past%20three%20years%20working%20for%20Chinese%20tech%20companies%20Alibaba%20and%20ByteDance%3Cp%3EYuri%20Zanoni%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EYuri%20Zanoni%20is%20a%20tech%20worker%20who%20made%20the%20switch%20from%20Amazon%20to%20Alibaba%20in%202020.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20the%20996%20work%20culture%20and%20numerous%20pandemic%20lockdowns%20were%20huge%20points%20of%20stress.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20after%20three%20years%2C%C2%A0he's%20certain%20that%20moving%20there%20was%20the%20right%20career%20move.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Yuri%20Zanoni%2C%20a%2033-year-old%20tech%20worker%20based%20in%20Shanghai.%20This%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20verified%20his%20employment%20and%20salary.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202019%2C%20I%20was%20living%20in%20Sao%20Paulo%20and%20working%20for%20Amazon%20when%20I%20got%20a%20LinkedIn%20message%20from%20an%20Alibaba%20recruiter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20looking%20for%20someone%20with%20e-commerce%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20working%20for%20their%20biggest%20competitor%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20who%20was%20willing%20to%20make%20the%20move%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20offer%20felt%20like%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%20They%20were%20offering%20compensation%20that%20was%20more%20than%20twice%20what%20I%20was%20making%20at%20Amazon%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20around%20%2425%2C000%20annually%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20several%20big%20steps%20up%20promotion-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20today%2C%20after%20three%20years%20of%20adapting%20to%20the%20intense%20work%20culture%20and%20numerous%20lockdowns%2C%20I've%20come%20to%20develop%20a%20real%20love-hate%20relationship%20with%20the%20work%20culture%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20from%20Sao%20Paulo%20to%20Hangzhou%20was%20an%20isolating%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221632%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Before%20moving%20to%20Mainland%20China%2C%20Yuri%20spent%20two%20years%20studying%20Mandarin%20in%20Taiwan%20as%20a%20university%20student.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655f68c44ca513d8242e0f0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221224%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBefore%20moving%20to%20Mainland%20China%2C%20Yuri%20spent%20two%20years%20studying%20Mandarin%20at%20the%20National%20Taiwan%20University%20while%20he%20was%20still%20a%20student.%3Cp%3EYuri%20Zanoni%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Hangzhou%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20few%20months%20of%20working%20in%20Hangzhou%20were%20terrifying.%20Besides%20my%20manager%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20my%20colleagues%20were%20proficient%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20was%20already%20proficient%20in%20some%20Mandarin%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20spent%20a%20few%20years%20learning%20it%20in%20Macau%20and%20Taiwan%20as%20a%20university%20student%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20nowhere%20near%20good%20enough%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20workplace%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20I%20was%20mainly%20working%20on%20Alibaba's%20Brazil%20operations%2C%20doing%20localisation%20work%20and%20content%20strategy.%20Despite%20often%20being%20the%20only%20Portuguese%20speaker%20in%20the%20room%2C%20my%20lack%20of%20Mandarin%20proficiency%20meant%20that%20I%20often%20couldn't%20convey%20my%20insights%20on%20the%20market%20I%20grew%20up%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20feeling%20really%20isolated%2C%20especially%20because%20I%20lived%20close%20to%20Alibaba's%20Campus%20%E2%80%94%20what%20we%20called%20the%20company's%20headquarters%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20far%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20city.%20I'd%20always%20lived%20in%20big%20cities%20before%2C%20so%20the%20loneliness%20was%20really%20affecting%20my%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina's%20996%20work%20culture%20introduced%20me%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20level%20of%20grind%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yuri%20during%20his%20time%20working%20at%20Alibaba%20on%20their%20eCommerce%20arm%2C%20AliExpress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655f68309c7d23cb3b9f35e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYuri%20during%20his%20time%20working%20at%20Alibaba%20on%20their%20eCommerce%20arm%2C%20AliExpress%3Cp%3EYuri%20Zanoni%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20other%20Chinese%20tech%20companies%2C%20Alibaba%20has%20an%20intense%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F996-work-culture-schedule-popular-in-china-explained-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E996%20work%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20means%20working%20from%209%20a.m.%20to%209%20p.m.%2C%20six%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20a%20big%20shock%20to%20me%20when%20I%20first%20moved%2C%20because%20I%20felt%20pressure%20to%20arrive%20before%20everyone%20and%20to%20stay%20until%20after%20my%20manager%20had%20left.%20If%20I%20wanted%20to%20leave%20early%2C%20I'd%20either%20have%20to%20sneak%20out%20of%20the%20office%20or%20get%20dinged%20on%20my%20performance%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20moving%20to%20Hangzhou%2C%20I%20had%20never%20seen%20people%20bring%20so%20much%20of%20their%20home%20into%20the%20office.%20My%20colleagues%20would%20bring%20into%20the%20office%20their%20mattresses%2C%20pillows%2C%20and%20quilts%2C%20along%20with%20a%20ton%20of%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20really%20new%20to%20me.%20I%20try%20to%20separate%20the%20personal%20from%20the%20professional%20in%20my%20life%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20shift%20from%20working%20at%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20after%20growing%20tired%20of%20the%20work%20culture%20and%20life%20in%20Hangzhou%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20I%20found%20wasn't%20the%20best%20city%20for%20a%2030-year-old%20single%20international%20to%20live%20in%C2%A0%E2%80%94%C2%A0I%20started%20looking%20for%20jobs%20in%20Shanghai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20in%20Shanghai%20was%20amazing%2C%20until%20the%20lockdowns%20came%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yuri%20during%20his%20first%20day%20at%20work%20at%20ByteDance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655f673e9c7d23cb3b9f35a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYuri%20during%20his%20first%20day%20at%20work%20at%20ByteDance%20in%202021%3Cp%3EYuri%20Zanoni%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Shanghai%20to%20start%20working%20for%20ByteDance%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20TikTok%2C%20as%20a%20content%20strategist.%20From%20the%20minute%20I%20moved%20there%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20the%20home%20I%20didn't%20even%20realize%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShanghai%20is%20more%20international%20than%20Hangzhou.%20It's%20a%20city%20you%20can%20really%20lose%20yourself%20in.%20There's%20so%20much%20going%20on%20culturally%20and%20in%20the%20nightlife%2C%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20city%20means%20that%20you%20can%20always%20reinvent%20yourself.%20Plus%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20