h%20their%20fighters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227903%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20F-35%20fighter%20jets%20flying%20in%20formation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525891755f52b01b35b454a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EF-35%20fighter%20jets%20fly%20in%20formation.%3Cp%3ERitzau%20Scanpix%2FBo%20Amstrup%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussia%2C%20China%2C%20and%20the%20US%20all%20have%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20jet%20programs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Russian%20Su-57%2C%20Chinese%20J-20%2C%20and%20American%20F-35%20are%20all%20facing%20various%20challenges.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20several%20experts%20about%20what's%20been%20holding%20these%20programs%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20top%20military%20powers%20have%20been%20working%20to%20develop%20formidable%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20jet%20fleets%20for%20decades%2C%20and%20that's%20still%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20built%20the%20first%20fifth-generation%20fighter%2C%20the%20stealth%20F-22%20Raptor%2C%20and%20it%20followed%20that%20project%20with%20the%20F-35%20Lightning%20II%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter.%20Russia%20and%20China%20have%20the%20Su-57%20and%20J-20%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20F-22%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20production%2C%20and%20the%20three%20newest%20jets%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20regarded%20as%20fifth-gen%20jets%20even%20if%20some%20of%20them%20don't%20quite%20check%20all%20the%20boxes%2C%20are%20each%20facing%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20qualify%20as%20a%20fifth-generation%20fighter%2C%20an%20aircraft%20needs%20to%20have%20certain%20features%20like%20stealth%20capabilities%20to%20avoid%20detection%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20cruise%20at%20supersonic%20speeds%20without%20engaging%20its%20afterburners%2C%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAviation%20experts%20outlined%20several%20issues%20with%20the%20Russian%2C%20Chinese%2C%20and%20American%20fifth-generation%20programs%20%E2%80%94%20including%20problems%20with%20stealth%20technology%2C%20engine%20development%2C%20and%20maintenance%20%E2%80%94%20in%20recent%20interviews%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia's%20Su-57%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sukhoi%20Su-57%20jet%20fighter%20performs%20during%20International%20military-technical%20forum%20%26quot%3BArmy-2020%26quot%3B%20at%20Kubinka%20airbase%20in%20Moscow%20Region%2C%20Russia%20August%2025%2C%202020.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65315bee96f7540cd06095e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221604%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESukhoi%20Su-57%20jet%20fighter%20performs%20during%20International%20military-technical%20forum%20%26quot%3BArmy-2020%26quot%3B%20at%20Kubinka%20airbase%20in%20Moscow%20Region%2C%20Russia%20August%2025%2C%202020.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FMaxim%20Shemetov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sukhoi%20Su-57%20is%20Russia's%20first%20attempt%20at%20a%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20but%20analysts%20have%20questioned%20if%20it%20actually%20qualifies%20for%20this%20distinction%20given%20its%20shortcomings%20in%20several%20key%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnown%20to%20NATO%20as%20the%20'Felon%2C'%20the%20Su-57%20was%20delivered%20to%20the%20Russian%20military%20in%202020.%20There%20are%20said%20to%20be%20only%2010%20aircraft%20in%20Moscow's%20arsenal%2C%20but%20state%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Fdefense%2F1352447%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider.com%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_campaign%3Dbusinessinsider.com%26utm_referrer%3Dbusinessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuggests%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20figure%20will%20increase%20to%2022%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024%20and%20jump%20again%20to%2076%20by%202028.%20It's%20unclear%20if%20those%20plans%20will%20hold%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Su-57%20first%20saw%20combat%20experience%20above%20Syria%20in%202018.%20Last%20year%2C%20Russian%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Fdefense%2F1496395%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20aircraft%20had%20seen%20combat%20experience%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20is%20backed%20up%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDefenceHQ%2Fstatus%2F1612337912091217920%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20Britain's%20defense%20ministry.%20But%20while%20the%20jets%20may%20have%20engaged%20in%20some%20standoff%20attacks%2C%20there%20isn't%20really%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flittle-evidence-for-russian-claims-about-su57-fighting-in-ukraine-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevidence%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20widespread%20Su-57%20employment%20in%20the%20ongoing%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223163%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sukhoi%20Su-57%20fighter%20jets%20perform%20at%20the%20MAKS%202019%20air%20show%20in%20Zhukovsky%2C%20outside%20Moscow%2C%20Russia%2C%20August%2027%2C%202019.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65315b7abe9edfa8eda4e65c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESukhoi%20Su-57%20fighter%20jets%20perform%20at%20the%20MAKS%202019%20air%20show%20in%20Zhukovsky%2C%20outside%20Moscow%2C%20Russia%2C%20August%2027%2C%202019.%3Cp%3ESputnik%2FAleksey%20Nikolskyi%2FKremlin%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20explanation%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20participation%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20war%20that%20fifth-generation%20jets%20were%20built%20for%20could%20be%20that%20the%20Russian%20jet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffifth-generation-jets-made-ukraine-war-russia-su-57-missing-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elacks%20the%20low-observable%20characteristics%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20would%20allow%20it%20to%20operate%20as%20a%20proper%20fifth-generation%20fighter.%20Issues%20with%20the%20aircraft%20include%20Moscow's%20apparent%20struggle%20to%20outfit%20it%20with%20stealth-capable%20engines%20and%20tightly%20placed%20body%20panels%20that%20would%20adequately%20reduce%20its%20radar%20signature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Russia's%20reluctance%20to%20use%20its%20Su-57s%20in%20Ukraine%20%26quot%3Bsuggests%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20confidence%20in%20the%20claimed%20stealth%20properties%20of%20the%20jet%2C%26quot%3B%20Justin%20Bronk%2C%20an%20airpower%20expert%20at%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20(RUSI)%20think%20tank%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20the%20aircraft%20can%20only%20carry%20an%20older%20variant%20of%20the%20R-77%20air-to-air%20missile.%20This%20has%20%26quot%3Bfolding%20grid%20fins%20that%20prevent%20it%20from%20being%20carried%20internally%20on%20the%20aircraft%20and%20hence%20compromises%20its%20stealth%20signature%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina's%20J-20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22China%20J-20%20fighter%20jet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653bd50a0487ff031cb06d6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJ-20%20fighter%20jets%20perform%20during%20Airshow%20China%202022%20at%20the%20Zhuhai%20Air%20Show%20Center%20on%20November%208%2C%202022.%3Cp%3EChen%20Jimin%2FChina%20News%20Service%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20as%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bpacing%20challenge%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20US%20military%2C%20also%20has%20a%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20program.%20Six%20years%20after%20making%20its%20first%20flight%2C%20China's%20Chengdu%20J-20%20entered%20service%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20it%20joined%20Beijing's%20inventory%20of%201%2C900%20fighter%20jets%20and%20has%20since%20been%20%26quot%3Boperationally%20fielded%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%202023%20Pentagon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.defense.gov%2F2023%2FOct%2F19%2F2003323409%2F-1%2F-1%2F1%2F2023-MILITARY-AND-SECURITY-DEVELOPMENTS-INVOLVING-THE-PEOPLES-REPUBLIC-OF-CHINA.PDF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20country's%20military%20power.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-j20-stealth-jet-isnt-dominating-doesnt-need-to-be-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20has%20built%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20200%20J-20s%20and%20is%20preparing%20several%20upgrades%20for%20the%20fighter%2C%20among%20them%20being%20the%20installation%20of%20domestically%20produced%20WS-15%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20capable%20WS-15%20is%20the%20engine%20that%20the%20J-20%20was%20originally%20supposed%20to%20have%20because%20it%20would%20allow%20the%20fighter%20to%20fly%20at%20supersonic%20speeds%20without%20engaging%20afterburners%20and%20lend%20the%20aircraft%20some%20additional%20stealth%20capabilities.%20But%20the%20Chinese%20defense%20industry%20has%20long%20struggled%20to%20manufacture%20the%20advanced%20engine%2C%20so%20the%20military%20has%20used%20older%20Chinese%20engines%20and%20Russian%20ones%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20J-20%20engines%20have%20been%20a%20big%20headache%2C%20but%20I%20think%20they're%20indicative%20of%20larger%20challenges%20within%20the%20Chinese%20defense%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mike%20Dahm%2C%20a%20former%20US%20Navy%20intelligence%20officer.%20%26quot%3BFor%20all%20of%20China's%20technological%20progress%2C%20they%20still%20lag%20behind%20the%20West%20in%20high-end%20manufacturing%20techniques%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20engines%2C%20low-observable%20materials%2C%20or%20metallurgy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrecision%20manufacturing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bhas%20an%20outsized%20impact%20on%20stealth%20and%20fifth-generation%20aircraft%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22China%20J-20%20stealth%20fighter%20jet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653bdd32356802a56be5f61a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20J-20%20stealth%20fighter%20jet%20in%20Changchun%20in%20China's%20Jilin%20Province%20on%20July%2024%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EWang%20Jingtian%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20earlier%20setbacks%2C%20the%20J-20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbreakingdefense.com%2F2023%2F07%2Fchina-j20-fighter-engine-ws15%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappeared%20to%20fly%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20pair%20of%20WS-15%20engines%20this%20past%20summer%20in%20a%20milestone%20moment.%20But%20Dahm%2C%20a%20senior%20resident%20fellow%20at%20the%20Mitchell%20Institute%20for%20Aerospace%20Studies%2C%20cautioned%20that%20even%20if%20China%20has%20managed%20to%20overcome%20its%20manufacturing%20challenges%2C%20the%20reliability%20of%20the%20WS-15%20engines%20is%20still%20questionable%20and%20could%20cause%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20it's%20not%20built%20to%20the%20same%20tolerances%20as%20Western%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20engine's%20lifetime%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20perform%20maintenance%20on%20their%20engines%20more%20often%20and%20will%20probably%20have%20to%20replace%20the%20engines%20more%20often%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20maintenance%20challenges%20will%20ultimately%20impact%20the%20readiness%20of%20the%20aircraft%20and%20the%20availability%20of%20the%20aircraft.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Bohnert%2C%20a%20licensed%20engineer%20at%20the%20RAND%20Corporation%20think%20tank%20who%20has%20supported%20analysis%20work%20for%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20said%20maintenance%20of%20stealth%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20like%20applying%20coating%20on%20an%20aircraft%20%E2%80%94%20is%20an%20expensive%20and%20%26quot%3Bpainful%26quot%3B%20process%20that%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20investment%2C%20both%20from%20a%20labor%20and%20infrastructure%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20stealth%20aircraft%20is%20more%20than%20just%20the%20plane%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohnert%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20missiles%2C%20the%20tactics%2C%20it's%20the%20logistics%2C%20it's%20the%20maintenance%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20lot%20that%20goes%20into%20it.%20It's%20a%20long%20train%20to%20get%20there%2C%20and%20you%20can%20choose%20not%20to%20follow%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20Russians%2C%20China%20is%20still%20relatively%20new%20to%20the%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20game.%20But%20even%20the%20US%2C%20which%20has%20had%20a%20fifth-gen%20jet%20since%202005%2C%20is%20having%20challenges%20with%20its%20new%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmerica's%20F-35%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Air%20Force%20F-35%20Middle%20East%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64999d70c218ba0019a80eed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221429%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20F-35s%20over%20the%20US%20Central%20Command%20area%20of%20responsibility%20on%20September%2030%2C%202020.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%2FSenior%20Airman%20Duncan%20Bevan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20by%20defense%20manufacturer%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20the%20F-35%20is%20the%20second%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20in%20America's%20arsenal%20after%20the%20F-22%20Raptor%20and%20comes%20in%20three%20variants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Marine%20Corps%20F-35B%20is%20capable%20of%20short%20takeoffs%20and%20vertical%20landings%20and%20was%20first%20achieved%20initial%20operational%20capability%20in%202015.%20The%20F-35A%20is%20used%20by%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20and%20achieved%20IOC%20in%202016%20while%20the%20F-35C%20is%20employed%20by%20the%20US%20Navy%20and%20was%20operational%20by%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%2C%20which%20was%20built%20for%20ground%20attacks%2C%20air-to-air%20combat%2C%20and%20networked%20airpower%2C%20has%20patrolled%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20Pacific%20and%20seen%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fair%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2Fus-air-force-conducts-airstrikes-with-f-35-for-first-time-ever%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecombat%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fifth-gen%20plane%20is%20operated%20by%20both%20the%20US%20military%20and%20a%20number%20of%20US%20allies.%20Israel%20was%20actually%20the%20first%20nation%20to%20fly%20the%20jet%20in%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20has%20around%20450%20F-35s%20and%20the%20Pentagon%20plans%20to%20procure%20approximately%202%2C500%20more%20over%20the%20next%20several%20decades%3B%20the%20estimated%20life%20cycle%20cost%20is%20more%20than%20%241.7%20trillion%20%E2%80%94%20much%20of%20which%20will%20go%20to%20operating%20and%20repairing%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20very%20expensive%20program%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20maintenance%20and%20sustainability%20issues%20that%20have%20often%20impacted%20the%20fighter%20jet's%20readiness%2C%20and%20that%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20case%2C%20according%20to%20a%20September%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gao.gov%2Fproducts%2Fgao-23-105341%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20the%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%2C%20or%20GAO.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20aircraft%20was%20capable%20of%20flying%20missions%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff35-fighters-mission-capable-just-over-half-the-time-watchdog-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebarely%20over%20half%20the%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20identified%20several%20specific%20issues%20at%20military%20installations%2C%20including%20a%20lack%20of%20support%20equipment%2C%20spare%20parts%2C%20adequate%20training%2C%20and%20technical%20data%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20can%20contribute%20to%20maintenance%20delays.%20The%20report%20also%20found%20that%20the%20F-35%20program%20was%20behind%20schedule%20in%20establishing%20facilities%20to%20conduct%20repairs%20and%20that%20the%20US%20government%20has%20relied%20heavily%20on%20contractors%2C%20which%20reduces%20its%20own%20ability%20to%20make%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20overarching%20problem%20is%20that%20for%20many%20years%2C%20the%20F-35%20program%20was%20focused%20on%20production%2C%20said%20Diana%20Maurer%2C%20the%20director%20of%20defense%20capabilities%20and%20management%20at%20the%20GAO.%20The%20priorities%20were%20largely%20about%20research%2C%20development%2C%20and%20acquisition%2C%20while%20sustainment%20and%20its%20costs%20were%20downgraded%20to%20a%20later%20focus.%20These%20problems%20are%20now%20in%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226390%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20US%20Air%20Force's%20F-35%20stealth%20fighter%20takes%20off%20for%20an%20aerial%20demonstration%20debut%20at%20the%20Le%20Bourget%20Airport%20during%20the%202017%20Paris%20Air%20Show%20on%20June%2019%2C%202017%2C%20in%20Paris%2C%20France.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654549ff3cc84b4dfafc4fb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224260%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20Air%20Force's%20F-35%20stealth%20fighter%20takes%20off%20for%20an%20aerial%20demonstration%20debut%20at%20the%20Le%20Bourget%20Airport%20during%20the%202017%20Paris%20Air%20Show%20on%20June%2019%2C%202017%2C%20in%20Paris%2C%20France.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Yuriko%20Nakao%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20F%2035%2C%20when%20it%20was%20becoming%20operationally%20available%20to%20the%20services%2C%20did%20not%20have%20the%20depot%20repair%20facilities%20up%20and%20running%20to%20fix%20the%20aircraft%20when%20it%20was%20needed%20to%20be%20repaired.%20Even%20now%2C%20the%20program%20is%20still%20years%20behind%20in%20completing%20depot%20standup%2C%26quot%3B%20Maurer%20said.%20This%20means%20that%20when%20major%20parts%20of%20the%20aircraft%20need%20to%20be%20repaired%20or%20replaced%2C%20they%20often%20times%20need%20to%20go%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20the%20original%20equipment%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20creates%20a%20lot%20of%20delays%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20And%20because%20it%20takes%20longer%20to%20repair%20those%20parts%2C%20the%20backlog%20grows%2C%20and%20the%20aircraft%20becomes%20%26quot%3Bless%20able%20to%20fly%20across%20the%20entire%20fleet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GAO%20has%20made%20several%20recommendations%20to%20the%20Pentagon%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20alleviate%20some%20of%20the%20challenges%2C%20including%20reassessing%20the%20breakdown%20between%20government%20and%20contractor%20responsibility.%20If%20there%20is%20any%20change%20to%20this%20balance%20of%20oversight%2C%20the%20GAO%20suggested%20in%20its%20September%20report%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20figure%20out%20what%20sort%20of%20technical%20data%20or%20intellectual%20property%20it%20might%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20F-35%20program's%20woes%2C%20a%20December%20GAO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gao.gov%2Fproducts%2Fgao-24-107177%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dusgao%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20determined%20that%20there%20are%20issues%20with%20the%20fighter's%20cooling%20system.%20In%20particular%2C%20it's%20overtasked%2C%20operating%20beyond%20what%20it's%20designed%20to%20do%2C%20which%20could%20increase%20wear%20on%20the%20engine%2C%20reduce%20its%20life%2C%20and%20add%20billions%20in%20maintenance%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20important%20for%20the%20US%20to%20get%20a%20grip%20on%20the%20F%2035%20program.%20When%20it%20is%20flying%2C%20we've%20heard%20from%20pilots%20that%20they're%20very%20happy%20with%20the%20capabilities%20of%20that%20weapon%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Maurer%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20not%20just%20the%20future%20of%20combat%20aviation%20for%20three%20of%20our%20military%20services%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20present.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-china-us-militaries-fifth-gen-fighter-jets-problems-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703334601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c9d167a3c8094d5dd9e07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-china-us-militaries-fifth-gen-fighter-jets-problems-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%2C%20China%2C%20and%20the%20US%20all%20have%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20jet%20programs%2C%20but%20each%20country%20is%20having%20issues%20with%20its%20jets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-china-us-militaries-fifth-gen-fighter-jets-problems-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Things%20you%20should%20do%20for%20your%20career%20before%20the%20year%20ends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20illustration%20of%20a%20woman%20balancing%20on%20a%20suitcase.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6585e912cefc010bea26d9a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Ryan%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E