ter%20media%20reports%20claimed%20the%20hijab%20ban%20has%20been%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20by%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government%20on%20wearing%20the%20hijab%20had%20triggered%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20event%20in%20Mysuru%20yesterday%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20had%20said%20women%20can%20wear%20the%20hijab%20if%20they%20want.%20The%20comment%20led%20to%20speculation%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20ordered%20to%20scrap%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20told%20reporters%20today%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20not%20formally%20issued%20any%20order%20to%20allow%20wearing%20the%20hijab%20in%20educational%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20done%20it%20yet%20(allowing%20hijab).%20One%20person%20asked%20me%20a%20question%2C%20and%20I%20replied%20to%20that.%20Yes%2C%20the%20government%20is%20considering%20to%20end%20the%20ban.%20But%20the%20matter%20will%20be%20discussed%20with%20government%20officers%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Siddaramaiah%20told%20reporters%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20to%20end%20the%20hijab%20ban%20was%20already%20on%20the%20Congress's%20agenda%20before%20the%20election%20in%20May%20this%20year%2C%20when%20the%20party%20defeated%20the%20BJP%20under%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Basavaraj%20Bommai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20attacked%20the%20BJP%20over%20allegedly%20dividing%20people%20based%20on%20what%20they%20wear%20and%20caste%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20called%20the%20Congress's%20policy%20%26quot%3Bappeasement%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hijab%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20delivered%20a%20split%20verdict%20on%20whether%20the%20government%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20make%20rules%20on%20what%20to%20wear.%20The%20court%20had%20said%20it%20would%20consider%20setting%20up%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20to%20take%20the%20matter%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20matter%20is%20pending%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20does%20not%20even%20take%20that%20into%20consideration%20and%20decides%20to%20please%20the%20minorities%2C%20while%20eyeing%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bommai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hijab%20row%20began%20in%20December%202021%20when%20six%20girls%20in%20Udupi's%20Government%20PU%20College%20were%20denied%20permission%20to%20wear%20the%20scarf%20in%20classrooms.%20It%20has%20now%20become%20another%20political%20issue%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703333220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2Fdl8l485g_karnataka-hijab-ban_625x300_22_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fnot-done-yet-karnataka-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-clarifies-after-big-hiijab-ban-statement-4728689%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20not%20given%20any%20order%20to%20end%20the%20ban%20on%20wearing%20the%20hijab%20in%20educational%20institutions%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20on%20Saturday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20media%20reports%20claimed%20the%20hijab%20ban%20has%20been%20removed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fnot-done-yet-karnataka-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-clarifies-after-big-hiijab-ban-statement-4728689%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fnot-done-yet-karnataka-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-clarifies-after-big-hiijab-ban-statement-4728689%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fnot-done-yet-karnataka-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-clarifies-after-big-hiijab-ban-statement-4728689%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Liquor%20in%20GIFT%20City%3A%20Oppn%20slams%20Gujarat's%20BJP%20govt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A170333304