%2Fstatus%2F1738206440685531179%5C%22%3Eordered%20the%20revocation%20of%20the%20ban%20on%20hijabs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20educational%20institutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%20at%20a%20function%20in%20Mysuru%20district%2C%20he%20said%20his%20government%20would%20revoke%20the%20ban%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20can%20wear%20the%20dress%20of%20their%20choice%E2%80%9D%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fkarnataka-chief-minister-says-he-has-asked-for-withdrawal-of-order-banning-hijab-in-classrooms%2Farticle67666503.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20instructed%20%5Bthe%20officials%5D%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20restriction%20from%20tomorrow%20%5BDecember%2023%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20South%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20portal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fkarnataka%2Fno-more-hijab-ban-says-karnataka-cm-siddaramaiah-adds-clothes-food-are-individual-choices%2F%5C%22%3Equoted%20him%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20last%20year%2C%20the%20state%20government%2C%20then%20controlled%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fjournal%2Fkarnataka-government-order-on-dress-code-for-students%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20students%20in%20government%20schools%20and%20in%20colleges%20falling%20under%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20pre-university%20education%20board%20must%20wear%20uniforms%20fixed%20by%20the%20state%20or%20the%20colleges%E2%80%99%20administrative%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20prohibited%20the%20use%20of%20clothes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthreaten%20equality%2C%20unity%2C%20and%20public%20order%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20female%20students%20at%20a%20pre-university%20college%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Udupi%20district%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewi