nce%20his%20Ranji%20Trophy%20debut%20in%202015%2C%20wouldn't%20even%20be%20in%20the%20picture%20had%20Shami%20been%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20hasn't%20done%20his%20cause%20any%20harm%20by%20picking%20up%20a%20fifer%20for%20India%20'A'%20against%20South%20Africa%20'A'%20in%20first%20'Unofficial%20Test'%20in%20Potchefstroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasidh%2C%20whose%20speed%20is%20a%20bit%20more%20and%20a%20natural%20length%20on%20the%20shorter%20side%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20get%20more%20bounce.%20But%20he%20can%20also%20leak%20runs%20as%20he%20is%20not%20known%20to%20be%20consistent%20with%20his%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20goes%20by%20form%20in%20ODIs%2C%20Mukesh%20could%20lose%20out%20but%20going%20by%20skills%20in%20red%20ball%20cricket%2C%20he%20does%20hold%20a%20distinct%20advantage%20over%20Prasidh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKL%20'the%20batter'%20or%20KL%20'the%20Keeper'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnSupersport%20Park%20was%20the%20venue%20where%20India%20won%20their%20only%20Test%20of%20the%20three-match%20series%20back%20in%202021.%20Rahul%20looked%20majestic%20en-route%20his%20hundred%20while%20opening%20the%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20have%20changed%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20Rahul%20lost%20his%20form%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20horrific%20accident%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KS%20Bharat%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F60643-kona-srikar-bharat-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKS%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20look%20cut%20out%20for%20top%20flight%20cricket%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20being%20benched%20since%20the%20start%20of%20World%20Cup%2C%20h