Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20allowing%20anybody%2C%20including%20the%20media%2C%20to%20enter%20the%20village.%20They%20have%20deployed%20CRPF%20men%20in%20large%20strength%20in%20the%20locality.%20This%20is%20the%20height%20of%20injustice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique%20said%20they%20were%20innocent%20and%20had%20not%20even%20remote%20links%20with%20any%20subversive%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20adverse%20against%20them.%20There%20is%20not%20even%20an%20application%20against%20them%20in%20the%20police%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoor%20Ahmad%2C%20brother%20of%20deceased%20Safeer%20Hussain%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20detained%20by%20Army%20men%20from%20his%20home%20on%20Friday.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20shocked%20to%20know%20in%20the%20evening%20that%20they%20had%20been%20killed.%20They%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20custody%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoor%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20talk.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20shock.%20I%20will%20talk%20to%20you%20after%20the%20funeral%20prayers%20are%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20purported%20video%20clips%20of%20the%20detained%20men%20being%20tortured%20show%20army%20soldiers%20spraying%20chilli%20powder%20on%20their%20buttocks.%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EGand%20Mein%20Dal%20Es%20Ko%20Mirchi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Put%20chilli%20in%20his%20anus)%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20soldier%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20also%20shows%20a%20young%20boy%2C%20who%20is%20lying%20motionless%20on%20the%20ground%20while%20another%20man%20can%20be%20seen%20moving%20his%20hands%20helplessly%20before%20being%20stripped%20and%20sprayed%20with%20chilli%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20shows%20army%20soldiers%20pushing%20and%20beating%20up%20a%20man%20with%20what%20looks%20like%20a%20plastic%20cane%20while%20he%20is%20pleading%20with%20them%20to%20spare%20him.%20An%20army%20man%20could%20be%20seen%20sitting%20with%20jackboots%20on%20the%20arms%20of%20a%20civilian%20lying%20motionless%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%20has%20been%20suspended%20in%20Poonch%20district%20following%20the%20alleged%20custodial%20deaths.%20Preparations%20are%20underway%20to%20conduct%20their%20last%20rites%20with%20top%20officials%20of%20civil%20and%20police%20administration%20rushing%20to%20the%20area%20while%20restrictions%20have%20been%20imposed%20to%20avoid%20any%20law%20and%20order%20disturbances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20visit%20their%20village%20because%20there%20are%20restrictions%20here.%20But%20I%20have%20been%20told%20that%20the%20five%20other%20civilians%20are%20admitted%20in%20the%20army%20hospital.%20We%20are%20preparing%20to%20conduct%20the%20last%20rites%20of%20the%20deceased%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rafiq%2C%20the%20Sarpanch%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20all%20labourers%20who%20struggled%20to%20make%20a%20living.%20I%20guarantee%20that%20they%20were%20not%20involved%20in%20any%20illegal%20activities.%20It%20is%20tragic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Divisional%20Commissioner%20Jammu%2C%20Ramesh%20Kumar%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20gathering%20details%20about%20how%20the%20civilians%20died.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20collecting%20details%2C%20will%20share%20it%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20population%20of%20around%20200-250%20population%20comprising%20largely%20Gujjar%20and%20Bakkerwal%20tribes%2C%20the%20village%20of%20Topa%20Mastandara%20is%20situated%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Dera%20Ki%20Gali-Bufliaz%20axis%20where%20two%20Army%20vehicles%20were%20ambushed