encounters%20involving%20civilians%2C%20militants%20and%20security%20forces%2C%20the%20theatre%20of%20insurgency%20has%20shifted%20to%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20where%2024%20militants%20were%20killed%20this%20year%20while%2021%20army%20soldiers%20also%20laid%20down%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20civilians%20have%20also%20been%20killed%20in%20conflict-related%20violence%20in%20the%20twin%20districts%20this%20year%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20124%20people%2C%20including%2083%20militants%20and%2028%20security%20personnel%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20due%20to%20the%20prevailing%20security%20situation%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20deceased%20are%20two%20army%20and%20police%20officers%2C%20including%20a%20Colonel%20and%20a%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20week-long%20Kokernag%20encounter%20in%20south%20Kashmir%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20three%20labourers%20from%20Rajouri%20district%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20staged%20gun%20battle%20by%20the%20Army%20in%20Amshipora%20village%20of%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shopian%20district%20and%20passed%20off%20as%20terrorists%2C%20reportedly%20for%20cash%20reward%20and%20quick%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20police%20investigation%2C%20an%20Army%20Captain%20identified%20as%20Bhoopendra%20Singh%20alias%20Major%20Basheer%20Khan%20had%20abducted%20the%20three%20young%20men%20in%20a%20private%20car%20from%20their%20rented%20accommodation%20at%20Chowgam%20Shopian%2C%20killed%20them%20and%20later%20planted%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20weapons%20and%20material%20on%20their%20dead%20bodies%20and%20tried%20to%20tag%20them%20as%20hardcore%20terrorists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703325532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44.png%22%2C%22originID%