Cn%3Cp%3EVijender%20Singh%2C%20India's%20first%20boxer%20to%20win%20an%20Olympics%20medal%2C%20also%20announced%20his%20support%20to%20Ms%20Malikkh%20yesterday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20parents%20of%20the%20daughters%20would%20be%20concerned%20that%20if%20an%20Olympic%20medallist%20is%20not%20given%20justice%2C%20how%20will%20we%20get%20it%3F%20The%20PM%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20and%20President%20all%20should%20come%20and%20answer%20why%20this%20happened...%20This%20raises%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20on%20the%20justice%20system%20and%20the%20democratic%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20Vijender%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20WFI%20boss%20Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20longtime%20aide%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20was%20WFI%20chief%20for%2012%20years.%20A%20six-time%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20had%20to%20step%20aside%20after%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20Ms%20Malikkh%2C%20accused%20him%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20women%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20into%20tears%20during%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%20two%20days%20ago%2C%20Commonwealth%20and%20Asian%20Games%20Gold%20medallist%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20alleged%20with%20Sanjay%20Singh%20heading%20the%20WFI%2C%20women%20wrestlers%20will%20continue%20to%20face%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20three%20wrestlers%20led%20a%20huge%20protest%20at%20Delhi's%20Jantar%20Mantar%2C%20demanding%20action%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20called%20off%20the%20protest%20after%20the%20government%20ordered%20a%20probe.%20The%20wrestlers%20were%20also%20assured%20that%20no%20aide%20or%20relative%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20contest%20the%20next%20polls%20of%20the%20wrestling%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Brij%20Bhushan's%20son%20Prateek%20and%20son-in-law%20Vishal%20Singh%20did%20not%20enter%20the%20contest%2C%20his%20aide%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20nomination%20was%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%