20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20succeeded%20him%20in%20the%20top%20post%20in%20elections%20held%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Olympic%20medallist%20and%20ace%20wrestler%20Sakshee%20Malikkh%20declared%20that%20she%20was%20quitting%20the%20sport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20another%20wrestler%20Bajrang%20Punia%20returned%20his%20Padma%20Shri%20to%20PM%20Modi.%20The%20Olympic%20medal-winning%20wrestler%20kept%20his%20Padma%20Shri%20medallion%20on%20a%20footpath%20at%20the%20Kartavya%20Path%20in%20Delhi.%20It%20was%20later%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%2C%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%2C%20won%20the%20election%20to%20the%20wrestling%20federation%20by%20a%20landslide%20on%20Thursday%2C%20defeating%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20Anita%20Sheoran%2C%20backed%20by%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers.%20Mr%20Singh%20scooped%2040%20of%20the%2047%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20Ms%20Malikkh%2C%20Mr%20Punia%2C%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20led%20a%20massive%20protest%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20Delhi%2C%20accusing%20Sharan%20Singh%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20several%20wrestlers%20and%20demanding%20action%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20was%20called%20off%20after%20the%20government%20ordered%20a%20probe%20and%20assured%20the%20wrestlers%20that%20no%20aide%20or%20relative%20of%20Sharan%20Singh%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20contest%20the%20subsequent%20polls%20of%20the%20wrestling%20body.%20While%20Brij%20Bhushan's%20son%20Prateek%20and%20son-in-law%20Vishal%20Singh%20did%20not%20enter%20the%20contest%2C%20his%20aide%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20nomination%20was%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%20has%20earlier%20served%20as%20the%20vice-president%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20wrestling%20body.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20the%20WFI's%20last%20executive%20council%20and%20its%20joint%20secretary%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A170332