mar%20led%20India%20to%20a%204-1%20series%20win%20over%20Australia%2C%20while%20the%20T20I%20series%20ended%20in%20a%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20true%2C%20the%20latest%20development%20could%20be%20a%20huge%20blow%20for%20both%20Team%20India%20and%20MI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20IPL%20auction%2C%20MI%20bought%20South%20Africa%20pacer%20Gerald%20Coetzee%20as%20their%20first%20buy.%20Coetzee%2C%20who%20had%20a%20base%20price%20of%20Rs%202%20crore%2C%20went%20to%20MI%20for%20Rs%205%20crore%20after%20bidding%20wars%20with%20RCB%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI%20further%20strengthened%20their%20pace%20battery%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20Sri%20Lankan%20pacers%20Dilshan%20Madushanka%20and%20Nuwan%20Thushara.%C2%A0MI%20also%20waited%20until%20the%20accelerator%20round%20to%20rope%20in%20Afghanistan%20all-rounder%20Mohammad%20Nabi%20at%20his%20base%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMI%20Retained%20players%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%2C%20Dewald%20Brevis%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20N.%20Tilak%20Varma%2C%20Tim%20David%2C%20Vishnu%20Vinod%2C%20Arjun%20Tendulkar%2C%20Shams%20Mulani%2C%20Nehal%20Wadhera%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Kumar%20Kartikeya%2C%20Piyush%20Chawla%2C%20Akash%20Madhwal%2C%20Jason%20Behrendorff%2C%20Romario%20Shepherd%20(from%20LSG)%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%20(C)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMI%20players%20bought%20at%20IPL%202024%20auction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerald%20Coetzee%20(Rs.%205%20crore)%2C%20Dilshan%20Madushanka%20(Rs.%204.60%20crore)%2C%20Shreyas%20Gopal%20(Rs.%2020%20lakh)%2C%20Nuwan%20Thushara%20(Rs.%204.80%20crore)%2C%20Naman%20Dhir%20(Rs.%2020%20lakh)%2C%20Anshul%20Kamboj%20(Rs.%2020%20lakh)%2C%20Mohammad%20Nabi%20(Rs.%201.5%20crore)%2C%20Shivalik%20Sharma%20(Rs.%2020%20lakh)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703320560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fh12ssaio_hardik-pandya-x_625x300_28_November_23.j