25%20of%20all%20internet%20users.%20Those%20that%20use%20social%20media%20use%20an%20average%20of%206.7%20different%20networks%20each%20month%2C%20spending%20an%20average%20of%202%20hours%20and%2024%20minutes%20on%20them%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20findings%20in%20the%20report%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Instagram%20emerged%20as%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20most%20users%20were%20inclined%20to%20remove.%20The%20data%20indicates%20that%20in%202023%2C%20a%20staggering%20number%20of%20over%201%20million%20individuals%20globally%20were%20actively%20searching%20for%20'how%20to%20delete%20my%20Instagram%20account'%20each%20month.%20This%20equates%20to%20more%20than%2012%2C500%20searches%20per%20100%2C000%20people%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20despite%20its%20origins%20as%20a%20digital%20scrapbook%2C%20Instagram%20has%20consistently%20maintained%20its%20position%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20social%20media%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20states%20that%20despite%20all%20this%20trend%2C%20the%20app%20still%20boasts%202.4%20billion%20active%20users%20worldwide.%20However%2C%20if%20a%20million%20people%20continue%20to%20seek%20deletion%20of%20their%20accounts%20every%20month%2C%20the%20'Instagrammable'%20bubble%20could%20burst%2C%20potentially%20altering%20its%20landscape%20within%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20Snapchat%2C%20which%20first%20launched%20in%202011.%20Almost%20130%2C000%20people%20have%20looked%20to%20delete%20their%20Snapchat%20account%20per%20month%20this%20year.%20And%20while%20this%20is%20significantly%20less%20than%20Instagram%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20large%20part%20of%20their%20750%20million%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703320140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F186j3rl8_social-media-app_625x300_23_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthis-is-the-most