to-pm-modi-returns-padma-shri-medal-as-brij-bhushans-aide-becomes-wfi-chief%2Fcid%2F1988762%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20police%20picked%20up%20both%20the%20letter%20and%20the%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunia%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20return%20the%20award%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20a%20tearful%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20another%20wrestler%2C%20announced%20her%20decision%20to%20quit%20wrestling%20following%20the%20election%20of%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20Along%20with%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20Punia%2C%20and%20Malik%20had%20led%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20former%20WFI%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20reflect%20on%20this%20day%2C%C2%A0these%20medals%20and%20awards%20hurt%20me%2C%20and%20I%20wonder%20why%20we%20were%20even%20given%20these%20when%20we%20fought%20for%20our%20daughters%20and%20sisters%2C%20and%20we%20failed.%20I%20feel%20that%20I%20am%20not%20suitable%20for%20this%20award.%20The%20federation%20was%20formed%20to%20support%20the%20players%2C%20not%20to%20demean%20and%20push%20them%20to%20the%20limits%20of%20retirement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punia%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20further%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrestler-bajrang-punia-says-he-is-returning-his-padma-shri-to-pm-modi-amid-wrestling-body-row-4722726%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20are%20not%20given%20due%20respect%2C%20I%20do%20not%20deserve%20this%20honour%20either.%20We%20were%20on%20the%20road%20for%2040%20days%2C%20but%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20government%20have%20not%20been%20fulfilled.%20Our%20fight%20is%20not%20against%20the%20government%2C%20but%20against%20an%20individual.%20I%20believe%20in%20the%20judiciary%20but%2C%20with%20what%20is%20happening%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20keep%20faith%20in%20the%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20not%20give%20up%20wrestling.%