%20Petroleum%20Corporation%20Limited%C2%A0since%20December%204.%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20Fisheries%20Department%20assessed%20compensation%20for%20fishers%20in%20the%20area%20due%20to%20the%20livelihood%20losses%20caused%20by%20the%20oil%20spill.%20The%20state%20government%20is%20expected%20to%20pay%20around%20Rs%20366%20lakh%20as%20compensation%2C%20and%20the%20CPCL%20has%20already%20paid%20more%20than%20Rs%207.5%20crore%20as%20compensation%20to%20the%20state%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%2C%20it%20told%20the%20NGT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20fishers%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20an%20amount%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20damaged%20boat%2C%20and%20Rs%2012%2C500%20per%20fisher%20family%20will%20not%20suffice%20for%20the%20losses%20they%20have%20incurred%20due%20to%20the%20oil%20spill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%204%2C%20during%20and%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Cyclone%20Michaung%2C%20oil%20from%20the%20CPCL%20began%20leaking%20into%20Kosasthalaiyar%20river%20in%20north%20Chennai%20via%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%20and%20storm%20drains.%20The%20oil%20also%20reached%20the%20Ennore%20estuary%2C%20a%20crucial%20fishing%20ground%20for%20local%20communities%20and%20an%20important%20breeding%20ground%20for%20fish.%20The%20oil%20trailed%20into%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20and%20covered%20an%20expanse%20of%2020%20square%20kilometers%2C%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2F20-tonnes-of-oil-soaked-soil-7000-litres-of-affected-water-removed-tn-govt-on-chennai-oil-spill%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOily%20water%2C%20sludge%2C%20tar%20balls%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20December%2020%2C%20per%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreentribunal.gov.in%2Fgen_pdf_test.php%3Ffilepath%3DL25ndF9kb2N1bWVudHMvbmd0L2Nhc2Vkb2Mvb3JkZXJzL0NIRU5OQUkvMjAyMy0xMi0yMS9jb3VydHMvMS9kYWlseS8xNzAzMjMyNjAzMTczMDkzNTk1MzY1ODU0NDViOWNiMDEucGRm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20to%20the%20NGT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20regarding%20the%20oil%20spill%20and%20its%20impacts%2C%20teams%20have%20skimmed%20105%2C280%20litres%20of%20oily%20water%20and%20removed%20393.7%20tonnes%20of%20oily%20sludge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20water%20and%20sludge%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20CPCL%20for%20treatment%20and%20disposal.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETeams%20also%20collected%20tar%20balls%20%E2%80%93%20amounting%20to%2012%20kilograms%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20beaches%20adjoining%20the%20Koraikuppam%20and%20Konankuppam%20fishing%20villages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2014%2C%20the%20TNPCB%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2F20-tonnes-of-oil-soaked-soil-7000-litres-of-affected-water-removed-tn-govt-on-chennai-oil-spill%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20the%20NGT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2020%20tonnes%20of%20oil-soaked%20soil%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20area%20so%20far%2C%20along%20with%207%2C000%20litres%20of%20oil%20mixed%20with%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20TNPCB%20also%20told%20the%20NGT%20on%20December%2021%20that%20tests%20of%20the%20surface%20and%20groundwater%20samples%20from%20various%20stretches%20collected%20on%20various%20dates%20showed%20that%20several%20parameters%20(including%20ammonia%2C%20ozone%20and%20benzene)%20were%20within%20the%20standards%20mentioned%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board.%20Canal%20cleaning%20has%20been%20completed%20in%20three%20stretches%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Nettukuppam%20to%20Ennore%20Bridge%2C%20Ennore%20Bridge%20to%20Railway%20bridge%2C%20and%20from%20the%20Railway%20bridge%20to%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20the%20total%20four%20stretches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBirds%2C%20mangroves%20affected%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBased%20on%20the%20NGT%E2%80%99s%20last%20order%2C%20the%20state%20government%20also%20provided%20some%20details%20of%20the%20impacts%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20on%20birds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20the%20government%2C%20a%20special%20team%20of%20officers%20from%20the%20state%20forest%20department%20inspected%20the%20site%20and%20are%20taking%20%E2%80%9Cremedial%20measures%20for%20affected%20avifauna%E2%80%9D.%20Though%20the%20team%20did%20not%20find%20any%20dead%20birds%2C%20it%20noticed%20that%20some%20birds%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccovered%20by%20%5Ban%5D%20oily%20substance%E2%80%9D.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20department%20is%20capturing%20birds%20that%20are%20weak%20and%20easy%20to%20capture%2C%20since%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20capture%20or%20trap%20the%20birds%20without%20causing%20any%20injuries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20environmentalists%20have%20been%20spotting%20several%20spot-billed%20pelicans%20covered%20in%20oil%20in%20some%20of%20the%20affected%20areas.%20Spot-billed%20pelicans%20are%20listed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cnear%20threatened%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20IUCN%20Red%20List%20of%20Threatened%20Species.%20In%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1BV-zovMlj%2F%3Figsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EInstagram%20post%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20birder%20and%20naturalist%20M.%20Yuvan%20spotted%2020%20oil-drenched%20pelicans%20at%20Adyar%2C%20Cooum%2C%20and%20Pallikaranai%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20found%20a%20few%20carcasses%20of%20pelicans%20in%20the%20Ennore%20estuary%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yuvan%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOil%20spills%20are%20a%20huge%20concern%20for%20waterbirds%20since%20oil%20sticks%20to%20their%20feathers.%20Birds%20try%20to%20preen%20it%20away%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Einadvertently%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20take%20in%20the%20toxic%20compounds%20which%20can%20be%20fatal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20TNPCB%20also%20reported%20to%20the%20NGT%20that%20it%20would%20require%20%E2%80%9Cspecial%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20which%20will%20take%20at%20least%20two%20months%20%E2%80%93%20to%20remove%20oil%20from%20the%20mangroves%20that%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20oil%20spill.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20CPCL%E2%80%99s%20report%20claimed%20that%20their%20inspection%20of%20the%20mangrove%20areas%20in%20the%20vicinity%20found%20that%20the%20interiors%20of%20the%20mangrove%20patches%20were%20not%20affected.%20However%2C%20they%20found%20traces%20of%20oil%2C%20along%20the%20outer%20line%20of%20the%20mangroves%20located%20near%20the%20mouth%20of%20the%20Buckingham%20canal.%20This%20will%20be%20cleaned%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20NIO%2C%20Goa%2C%20CPCL%20told%20the%20NGT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20TNPCB%20told%20the%20NGT%20that%20there%20were%20no%20tar%20balls%20in%20the%20Pulicat%20lake%20near%20the%20fish%20landing%20centre.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20NGT%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Fngt-questions-tn-government-on-how-oil-spill-reached-pulicat-backwaters%2Farticle67651636.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Easked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20state%20government%20how%20the%20oil%20spill%20had%20reached%20the%20Pulicat%20backwaters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECompensation%20for%20fishers%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFishers%20can%20resume%20their%20fishing%20activities%20after%20the%20oil%20sludge%20in%20the%20fish%20landing%20centre%2C%20fish%20landing%20points%20and%20creek%20has%20been%20completed%2C%20and%20their%20boats%20and%20nets%20cleaned%2C%20the%20Fisheries%20Department%20told%20the%20NGT.%20However%2C%20the%20deadline%20for%20this%20has%20not%20been%20listed%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20department%20also%20told%20the%20NGT%20that%20a%20relief%20amount%20of%20Rs%2012%2C500%20(Rs%207%2C500%20from%20CPCL%20and%20Rs%205000%20from%20the%20state%20government)%20should%20be%20paid%20to%20fishers%20for%20the%20loss%20that%20the%20oil%20spill%20has%20caused%20to%20the%20livelihood%20of%20fisherfolk%20in%20the%20area.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20oil%20spill%20has%20not%20only%20prevented%20fishers%20from%20using%20their%20boats%2C%20as%20the%20oil%20sticks%20to%20and%20damages%20them%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20hindered%20their%20ability%20to%20fish%20in%20the%20polluted%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoat%20owners%20will%20be%20paid%20Rs%2010%2C000%20each%20for%20the%20damage%20to%20their%20boats%2C%20per%20the%20department.%20The%20department%20has%20assessed%20a%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%203.66%20crore%2C%20and%20a%20request%20for%20financial%20sanction%20of%20the%20amount%20has%20been%20made%20to%20the%20government%2C%20as%20communicated%20to%20the%20NGT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Additionally%2C%20the%20CPCL%20has%20agreed%20to%20pay%20more%20than%20Rs%207%20crore%20towards%20compensation%20for%20fishermen%2C%20and%20the%20CPCL%20has%20already%20paid%20this%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20State%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20as%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20fishers%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20compensation%20amounts%20(of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20damaged%20boat%2C%20and%20Rs%2012%2C500%20per%20fisher%20family)%20will%20not%20suffice%20for%20the%20losses%20they%20have%20incurred.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20amount%20works%20as%20a%20stop-gap%20arrangement%2C%20a%20temporary%20compensation%2C%20but%20this%20does%20not%20suffice%20for%20the%20losses%20we%20have%20faced%20due%20to%20the%20oil%20spill%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20R.L.%20Srinivasan%2C%20a%20fisherman%20who%20hails%20from%20Kattukuppam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20affected%20villages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESunlight%20that%20falls%20on%20their%20oil-caked%20boats%20will%20cause%20bubbles%20on%20the%20boat%20exteriors%20and%20interior%2C%20which%20will%20later%20develop%20into%20cracks%2C%20Srinivasan%20explained.%20And%20how%20can%20we%20feed%20our%20families%20for%20the%20next%20few%20months%20with%20a%20compensation%20of%20just%20Rs%2012%2C500%20per%20family%2C%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20take%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20months%20for%20us%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20back%20to%20our%20normal%20fishing%20routines%20and%20catch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20is%20our%20last%20resort%2C%20and%20we%20pray%20that%20they%20will%20release%20more%20funds%20to%20see%20us%20through%20this%20time.%20Then%20our%20trust%20in%20the%20government%20will%20increase%20too.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaybe%20the%20government%20can%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20this%20appeal%20to%20compensate%20us%20more%20fairly%2C%20Srinivasan%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NGT%20also%20expressed%20displeasure%20with%20the%20cleaning%20of%20houses%20done%20by%20the%20CPCL.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRegarding%20the%20cleaning%20of%20the%20residences%20and%20other%20small%20establishments%2C%20the%20method%20adopted%20by%20CPCL%20is%20not%20appreciated%20as%20the%20same%20can%20be%20broken%20only%20by%20using%20enzymes%20and%20requested%20such%20kind%20of%20cleaning%20method%20to%20be%20adopted.%20Besides%2C%20even%20in%20the%20soil%2C%20the%20oil%20has%20dispersed%20up%20to%2001%20or%2002%20feet%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20expert%20team%20of%20the%20TNPCB%20is%20examining%20the%20various%20causes%20in%20the%20cleaning%20process%20on%20land%20and%20in%20water%2C%20the%20government%20told%20the%20NGT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETowards%20a%20%E2%80%98workable%20solution%E2%80%99%20to%20prevent%20future%20disasters%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20these%20issues%2C%20the%20NGT%20has%20ordered%20that%20the%20cleaning%20process%20of%20the%20oil%20sludge%20be%20completed%20%E2%80%9Cas%20expeditiously%20as%20possible%E2%80%9D.%20It%20has%20also%20ordered%20the%20state%20government%20to%20file%20an%20interim%20report%2C%20before%20the%20next%20hearing%2C%20on%20the%20bio-remediation%20being%20undertaken%20by%20the%20government%20for%20cleaning%20the%20oil%20spill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NGT%20has%20also%20ordered%20the%20TNPCB%20to%20watch%20the%20north%20of%20the%20south%20gate%20for%20oil%20leakage%20and%20identify%20any%20new%20location%20of%20oil%20leakage%20and%20prevent%20it%20from%20spilling%20into%20the%20water%20bodies.%20It%20has%20also%20suggested%20that%20based%20on%20the%20case%20and%20related%20actions%2C%20the%20government%20comes%20up%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Cworkable%20solution%E2%80%9D%20along%20with%20the%20Manali%20Industries%20Association%20so%20that%20it%20can%20%E2%80%9Chelp%20in%20avoiding%20any%20future%20disaster%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NGT%20will%20again%20hear%20the%20case%20on%20January%2011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703256830000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15224024%2F2023_12_09_15_30_03_654-1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Foil-tar-balls-removed-after-north-chennai-oil-spill-but-birds-mangroves-affected-tn-govt-to-ngt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chennai%20Petroleum%20Corporation%20Limit